Easy install steps using the Android Package File (aka APK file):

1)Download the Androxplorer File Manager or any File Manager of your preference on your android powered device. (Link to Androxplorer: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=net.adisasta.androxplorer&feature=nav_result#?t=W251bGwsMSwxLDMsIm5ldC5hZGlzYXN0YS5hbmRyb3hwbG9yZXIiXQ.. )

2)Copy the travelguide.apk file from the system to your mobile device. You can copy the file over usb cable or bluetooth or by email&download.

3)Using the File Manager app on the adroid device, navigate to the copied travelguide APK file.

4)Select the travelguide.apk file and follow the on screen instructions to open and install the application.
